					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I'll be honest, I'm a big dum dum and didn't realize what was going on until I read your spoiler.</p> <p>However, this is written so well that I was absorbed into it from beginning to end. The clinical tone is immaculate without also being dry and boring.</p> <p>Honestly, I've very, very impressed.</p> <p>Great job!</p> <p><span style="text-decoration: line-through;">Also that banner is real nice.</span></p> 
				 	]]>
