						 <blockquote> <p>Archdemon Researcher C. Angra Mainyu D</p> </blockquote> <p>I saw this and scratched my head for a second before going back to this:</p> <blockquote> <p>Despite the danger presented by SCP-4318, it is noted that in other observed realities, SCP-4318 is distinguished by its apparent generative, biological necessity.</p> </blockquote> <p>&#8230;which lead me to realize what was going on here.</p> <p>Good stuff, I rather enjoyed this. +1</p> 
				 	]]>
